    "Connect your strap for haptic guidance , you'll feel one pulse on the inhale, two on the exhale, so you can breathe with your eyes closed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verbinde deinen Strap für haptische Führung , du spürst einen Impuls beim Einatmen, zwei beim Ausatmen, sodass du mit geschlossenen Augen atmen kannst."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connect your strap for haptic guidance , you'll feel one pulse on the inhale, two on the exhale, so you can breathe with your eyes closed."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Conecta tu pulsera para recibir guía háptica: sentirás un pulso al inhalar y dos al exhalar, para que puedas respirar con los ojos cerrados."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connectez votre bracelet pour un guidage haptique , vous sentirez une impulsion à l'inspiration, deux à l'expiration, pour respirer les yeux fermés."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Collega la tua fascia per la guida aptica, sentirai un impulso durante l'inspirazione e due durante l'espirazione, così puoi respirare a occhi chiusi."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Подключите браслет, чтобы он подсказывал ритм вибрацией: один импульс на вдохе, два , на выдохе. Так можно дышать с закрытыми глазами."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "连接你的手环以获得触感引导——吸气时一次脉冲，呼气时两次，让你闭着眼也能跟着呼吸。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "連接你的手環以獲得觸感引導——吸氣時一次脈衝，呼氣時兩次，讓你閉著眼也能跟著呼吸。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Connect your strap for haptic guidance — you'll feel one pulse on the inhale, two on the exhale, so you can breathe with your eyes closed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Collega la tua fascia per la guida aptica, sentirai una vibrazione durante l'inspirazione, due durante l'espirazione, così puoi respirare a occhi chiusi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "连接你的手环以获得触感引导 — 吸气时一次脉冲，呼气时两次，让你闭着眼也能跟着呼吸。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "連接你的手環以獲得觸感引導 — 吸氣時一次脈衝，呼氣時兩次，讓你閉著眼也能跟著呼吸。"
