    "I have read and accept these terms, and I'm using NOOP with my own device and my own data, at my own risk.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ho letto e accetto questi termini e sto usando NOOP con il mio dispositivo e i miei dati, a mio rischio."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我已阅读并接受这些条款，并且我是在自担风险的情况下，使用我自己的设备和我自己的数据来使用 NOOP。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我已閱讀並接受這些條款，並且我是在自擔風險的情況下，使用我自己的裝置和我自己的資料來使用 NOOP。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I keep this project anonymous, so crypto is the only way to chip in , no Patreon, no PayPal, no name attached. Quick, global, and private for both of us.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ich halte dieses Projekt anonym, daher ist Krypto die einzige Möglichkeit, beizutragen , kein Patreon, kein PayPal, kein Name. Schnell, weltweit und privat für uns beide."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I keep this project anonymous, so crypto is the only way to chip in , no Patreon, no PayPal, no name attached. Quick, global, and private for both of us."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantengo este proyecto de forma anónima, así que las criptomonedas son la única forma de contribuir: sin Patreon, sin PayPal, sin nombres. Rápido, global y privado para ambos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Je maintiens ce projet anonyme, donc la crypto est le seul moyen de contribuer , pas de Patreon, pas de PayPal, pas de nom attaché. Rapide, mondial et privé pour nous deux."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantengo questo progetto anonimo, quindi le cripto sono l'unico modo per contribuire, niente Patreon, niente PayPal, nessun nome collegato. Veloce, globale e privato per entrambi."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Проект остаётся анонимным, поэтому поддержать его можно только криптовалютой: без Patreon, PayPal и привязки к имени. Это быстро, доступно из любой страны и приватно для нас обоих."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我让这个项目保持匿名，所以加密货币是唯一的支持方式——没有 Patreon，没有 PayPal，不附带任何名字。快捷、全球通用，对你我双方都私密。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我讓這個專案保持匿名，所以加密貨幣是唯一的支持方式——沒有 Patreon，沒有 PayPal，不附帶任何名字。快捷、全球通用，對你我雙方都私密。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I keep this project anonymous, so crypto is the only way to chip in — no Patreon, no PayPal, no name attached. Quick, global, and private for both of us.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantengo questo progetto anonimo, quindi le criptovalute sono l'unico modo per contribuire, niente Patreon, niente PayPal, nessun nome collegato. Veloce, globale e privato per entrambi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我让这个项目保持匿名，所以加密货币是唯一的支持方式 — 没有 Patreon，没有 PayPal，不附带任何名字。快捷、全球通用，对你我双方都私密。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我讓這個專案保持匿名，所以加密貨幣是唯一的支持方式 — 沒有 Patreon，沒有 PayPal，不附帶任何名字。快捷、全球通用，對你我雙方都私密。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I understand this disconnects the ring from Oura and that NOOP cannot undo it for me.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capisco che questo scollega l'anello da Oura e che NOOP non può annullarlo per me."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白这会将戒指从 Oura 断开连接，并且 NOOP 无法为我撤销此操作。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白這會將戒指從 Oura 中斷連接，並且 NOOP 無法為我撤銷此操作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I understand this disconnects the ring from Oura and that NOOP cannot undo it for me. To go back to Oura I would factory-reset the ring again and set it up in the Oura app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capisco che questo scollega l'anello da Oura e che NOOP non può annullarlo per me. Per tornare a Oura dovrei ripristinare di nuovo l'anello alle impostazioni di fabbrica e configurarlo nell'app Oura."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白这会将戒指从 Oura 断开连接，并且 NOOP 无法为我撤销此操作。若要回到 Oura，我需要再次将戒指恢复出厂设置，并在 Oura 应用中重新设置它。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白這會將戒指從 Oura 中斷連接，並且 NOOP 無法為我撤銷此操作。若要回到 Oura，我需要再次將戒指恢復原廠設定，並在 Oura 應用程式中重新設定它。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I understand this is an experimental wellness feature, not a medical device or a diagnosis.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capisco che questa è una funzionalità sperimentale per il benessere, non un dispositivo medico né una diagnosi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白这是一项实验性的健康功能，而非医疗设备或诊断。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我明白這是一項實驗性的健康功能，而非醫療裝置或診斷。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I'm awake": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sono sveglio"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我醒了"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我醒了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "INBOX": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "POSTA IN ARRIVO"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "收件箱"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "收件匣"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Idle": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inattivo"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "空闲"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "閒置"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If it's saving you a subscription, a suggested $50+ — a fraction of a year of WHOOP — genuinely keeps the project alive. Anything is appreciated. Crypto only; the project stays anonymous.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se ti fa risparmiare un abbonamento, un suggerimento di $50+, una frazione di un anno di WHOOP, mantiene davvero vivo il progetto. Qualsiasi cifra è apprezzata. Solo cripto; il progetto resta anonimo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果它为你省下了一笔订阅费，建议捐赠 50 美元以上 — 只是 WHOOP 一年费用的一小部分 — 就能实实在在地让这个项目存活下去。任何金额都令人感激。仅限加密货币；项目保持匿名。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果它為你省下了一筆訂閱費，建議捐贈 50 美元以上 — 只是 WHOOP 一年費用的一小部分 — 就能實實在在地讓這個專案存活下去。任何金額都令人感激。僅限加密貨幣；專案保持匿名。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If the Oura app is still running it will hold the ring and adoption will fail. Force-quit Oura, then scan.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se l'app Oura è ancora in esecuzione manterrà l'anello e l'adozione fallirà. Forza la chiusura di Oura, poi scansiona."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果 Oura 应用仍在运行，它会占用戒指，接管将会失败。请强制退出 Oura，然后扫描。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果 Oura 應用程式仍在執行，它會佔用戒指，接管將會失敗。請強制退出 Oura，然後掃描。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you don't see the prompt, enable NOOP under Settings › Health › Data Access & Devices.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se non vedi la richiesta, abilita NOOP in Impostazioni › Salute › Accesso ai dati e dispositivi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你没有看到提示，请在「设置 › 健康 › 数据访问与设备」下启用 NOOP。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你沒有看到提示，請在「設定 › 健康 › 資料存取與裝置」下啟用 NOOP。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you don't see the prompt, turn NOOP on under Settings › Health › Data Access & Devices.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se non vedi la richiesta, attiva NOOP in Impostazioni › Salute › Accesso ai dati e dispositivi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你没有看到提示，请在「设置 › 健康 › 数据访问与设备」下打开 NOOP。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你沒有看到提示，請在「設定 › 健康 › 資料存取與裝置」下打開 NOOP。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you extracted your ring's 16-byte key from a previous Oura setup, NOOP can talk to the ring with that key without resetting it, so the Oura app keeps working too. NOOP does not extract keys for you and cannot help you find one. If you do not know what this means, go back and use the standard setup or file import.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se hai estratto la chiave da 16 byte del tuo anello da una precedente configurazione Oura, NOOP può comunicare con l'anello usando quella chiave senza ripristinarlo, così anche l'app Oura continua a funzionare. NOOP non estrae le chiavi per te e non può aiutarti a trovarne una. Se non sai cosa significhi, torna indietro e usa la configurazione standard o l'importazione da file."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你从之前的 Oura 设置中提取了戒指的 16 字节密钥，NOOP 可以用该密钥与戒指通信而无需重置它，因此 Oura 应用也能继续工作。NOOP 不会为你提取密钥，也无法帮你找到密钥。如果你不明白这是什么意思，请返回并使用标准设置或文件导入。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果你從之前的 Oura 設定中提取了戒指的 16 位元組金鑰，NOOP 可以用該金鑰與戒指通信而無需重置它，因此 Oura 應用程式也能繼續工作。NOOP 不會為你提取金鑰，也無法幫你找到金鑰。如果你不明白這是什麼意思，請返回並使用標準設定或檔案匯入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Imperial": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Imperiale"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "英制"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "英制"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import a WHOOP export, Apple Health or a second band and your best-sourced record builds here — on this device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importa un'esportazione WHOOP, Apple Health o una seconda fascia e il tuo record dalle migliori sorgenti si costruisce qui, su questo dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "导入一份 WHOOP 导出文件、Apple 健康或第二条手环，你的最佳来源记录便会在这里构建 — 就在这台设备上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匯入一份 WHOOP 匯出檔案、Apple 健康或第二條手環，你的最佳來源記錄便會在這裡建立 — 就在這台裝置上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import readings": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importa letture"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "导入读数"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匯入讀數"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import temp files": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importa file temporanei"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "导入临时文件"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匯入暫存檔案"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import your history first. A WHOOP export in Data Sources fills every metric you can explore here in about a minute.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importiere zuerst deine Historie. Ein WHOOP-Export unter Datenquellen füllt in etwa einer Minute jede Metrik, die du hier erkunden kannst."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Import your history first. A WHOOP export in Data Sources fills every metric you can explore here in about a minute."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importa primero tu historial. Una exportación de WHOOP en Fuentes de datos rellena en aproximadamente un minuto todas las métricas que puedes explorar aquí."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importez d'abord votre historique. Un export WHOOP dans Sources de données remplit toutes les métriques que vous pouvez explorer ici en environ une minute."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importa prima la tua cronologia. Un'esportazione WHOOP in Sorgenti dati riempie in circa un minuto ogni metrica che puoi esplorare qui."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Сначала импортируйте историю. Данные WHOOP из раздела «Источники данных» примерно за минуту заполнят все показатели, доступные для анализа здесь."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请先导入你的历史。在「数据来源」中导入一份 WHOOP 导出文件，约一分钟即可填满这里可以探索的每一项指标。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "請先匯入你的歷史。在「資料來源」中匯入一份 WHOOP 匯出檔案，約一分鐘即可填滿這裡可以探索的每一項指標。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Imported": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importato"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "已导入"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "已匯入"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Importing overwrites everything currently on %@. Your old data is kept in a side file just in case. NOOP needs a relaunch for an import to take effect. Export CSV writes a WHOOP-format zip of your days, sleeps, workouts and journal that re-imports into NOOP on Mac, iPhone, or Android — on-device computed rows are marked APPROXIMATE in its Source column; the full backup stays the lossless restore path.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'importazione sovrascrive tutto ciò che è attualmente su %@. I tuoi vecchi dati vengono conservati in un file separato per sicurezza. NOOP deve essere riavviato perché un'importazione abbia effetto. Esporta CSV scrive uno zip in formato WHOOP dei tuoi giorni, sonni, allenamenti e diario che si reimporta in NOOP su Mac, iPhone o Android, le righe calcolate sul dispositivo sono contrassegnate come APPROSSIMATIVE nella sua colonna Sorgente; il backup completo resta il percorso di ripristino senza perdite."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "导入会覆盖 %@ 上当前的所有内容。以防万一，你的旧数据会保存在一个备用文件中。导入生效需要重新启动 NOOP。导出 CSV 会写出一个 WHOOP 格式的 zip，包含你的每日数据、睡眠、锻炼和日志，可重新导入到 Mac、iPhone 或 Android 上的 NOOP 中 — 设备端计算的行会在其「来源」列中标为 APPROXIMATE（近似）；完整备份仍是无损的还原路径。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匯入會覆蓋 %@ 上目前的所有內容。以防萬一，你的舊資料會保存在一個備用檔案中。匯入生效需要重新啟動 NOOP。匯出 CSV 會寫出一個 WHOOP 格式的 zip，包含你的每日資料、睡眠、鍛鍊和日誌，可重新匯入到 Mac、iPhone 或 Android 上的 NOOP 中 — 裝置端計算的列會在其「來源」欄中標為 APPROXIMATE（近似）；完整備份仍是無損的還原路徑。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Importing overwrites everything currently on this Mac. Your old data is kept in a side file just in case. NOOP needs a relaunch for an import to take effect.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Import überschreibt alles, was sich derzeit auf diesem Mac befindet. Deine alten Daten werden sicherheitshalber in einer separaten Datei aufbewahrt. NOOP muss neu gestartet werden, damit ein Import wirksam wird."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importing overwrites everything currently on this Mac. Your old data is kept in a side file just in case. NOOP needs a relaunch for an import to take effect."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Importar sobrescribe todo lo que hay actualmente en este Mac. Tus datos antiguos se guardan en un archivo aparte por si acaso. NOOP necesita reiniciarse para que una importación tenga efecto."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'importation écrase tout ce qui se trouve actuellement sur ce Mac. Vos anciennes données sont conservées dans un fichier annexe au cas où. NOOP doit être relancé pour qu'une importation prenne effet."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'importazione sovrascrive tutto ciò che è attualmente su questo Mac. I tuoi vecchi dati vengono conservati in un file a parte per sicurezza. NOOP deve essere riavviato perché l'importazione abbia effetto."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "При импорте все текущие данные на этом Mac будут перезаписаны. Старые данные на всякий случай сохранятся в отдельном файле. Чтобы импорт вступил в силу, перезапустите NOOP."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "导入会覆盖这台 Mac 上当前的所有内容。以防万一，你的旧数据会保存在一个备用文件中。导入生效需要重新启动 NOOP。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "匯入會覆蓋這台 Mac 上目前的所有內容。以防萬一，你的舊資料會保存在一個備用檔案中。匯入生效需要重新啟動 NOOP。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
