    "Make %@ your active device now? It will provide your live data. You can change this any time.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rendere %@ il tuo dispositivo attivo ora? Fornirà i tuoi dati in diretta. Puoi cambiarlo in qualsiasi momento."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "现在将 %@ 设为你的活跃设备？它将提供你的实时数据。你可以随时更改。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "現在將 %@ 設為你的活躍裝置？它將提供你的即時資料。你可以隨時更改。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make %@ your active strap? From now on it provides your live data. %@'s history stays exactly as it is — only new days come from %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Make %1$@ your active strap? From now on it provides your live data. %2$@'s history stays exactly as it is — only new days come from %3$@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rendere %1$@ la tua fascia attiva? D'ora in poi fornirà i tuoi dati in diretta. La cronologia di %2$@ resta esattamente com'è, solo i nuovi giorni provengono da %3$@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将 %1$@ 设为你的活跃手环？从现在起，它将提供你的实时数据。%2$@ 的历史保持原样 — 只有新的日期来自 %3$@。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "將 %1$@ 設為你的活躍手環？從現在起，它將提供你的即時資料。%2$@ 的歷史保持原樣 — 只有新的日期來自 %3$@。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make active": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rendi attiva"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "设为活跃"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "設為活躍"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make sure it's awake and not connected elsewhere.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Assicurati che sia attiva e non connessa altrove."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "确保它已唤醒且未在别处连接。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "確保它已喚醒且未在別處連接。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make the strap do things , tap to act, walk away to lock, train by feel.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lass den Strap Dinge tun , tippen zum Auslösen, weggehen zum Sperren, nach Gefühl trainieren."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Make the strap do things , tap to act, walk away to lock, train by feel."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haz que la correa haga cosas: toca para actuar, aléjate para bloquear, entrena por sensaciones."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Faites faire des choses au bracelet , tapez pour agir, éloignez-vous pour verrouiller, entraînez-vous au ressenti."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fai fare cose alla fascia, tocca per agire, allontanati per bloccare, allenati a sensazione."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Настройте действия браслета: коснитесь, чтобы выполнить команду; отойдите, чтобы заблокировать; тренируйтесь, ориентируясь по сигналам."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "让手环为你做事——轻点执行，走开即锁定，凭感觉训练。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "讓手環為你做事——輕點執行，走開即鎖定，憑感覺訓練。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make the strap do things — tap to act, walk away to lock, train by feel.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fai fare cose alla fascia, tocca per agire, allontanati per bloccare, allenati a sensazione."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "让手环为你做事 — 轻点执行，走开即锁定，凭感觉训练。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "讓手環為你做事 — 輕點執行，走開即鎖定，憑感覺訓練。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make this your active device?": {
      "localizations": {
