            "value": "无 HRV 数值"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無 HRV 數值"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No SpO₂ import or Health value": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessuna importazione SpO₂ o valore Health"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无 SpO₂ 导入或健康数值"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無 SpO₂ 匯入或健康數值"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No WHOOP? You can still continue. Pair a heart-rate strap (Polar, Wahoo, Coospo, Garmin HRM…) or a gym machine under Devices, or import from WHOOP, Apple Health, Oura, Fitbit, Garmin and more under Data Sources. You can do either any time.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Niente WHOOP? Puoi comunque continuare. Abbina una fascia cardio (Polar, Wahoo, Coospo, Garmin HRM…) o una macchina da palestra in Dispositivi, oppure importa da WHOOP, Apple Health, Oura, Fitbit, Garmin e altro in Sorgenti dati. Puoi fare entrambe le cose in qualsiasi momento."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "没有 WHOOP？你仍然可以继续。在「设备」下配对一条心率带（Polar、Wahoo、Coospo、Garmin HRM…）或一台健身房器械，或在「数据来源」下从 WHOOP、Apple 健康、Oura、Fitbit、Garmin 等导入。两者你都可以随时进行。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "沒有 WHOOP？你仍然可以繼續。在「裝置」下配對一條心率帶（Polar、Wahoo、Coospo、Garmin HRM…）或一台健身房器械，或在「資料來源」下從 WHOOP、Apple 健康、Oura、Fitbit、Garmin 等匯入。兩者你都可以隨時進行。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No backup yet.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessun backup."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚无备份。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚無備份。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No biometrics yet. Import your WHOOP export (and Apple Health if you have it) in Data Sources to fill this in.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch keine Biometrie. Importiere deinen WHOOP-Export (und Apple Health, falls vorhanden) unter Datenquellen, um dies zu füllen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No biometrics yet. Import your WHOOP export (and Apple Health if you have it) in Data Sources to fill this in."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aún no hay datos biométricos. Importa tu exportación de WHOOP (y Apple Health si lo tienes) en Fuentes de datos para rellenar esto."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pas encore de données biométriques. Importez votre export WHOOP (et Apple Santé si vous l'avez) dans Sources de données pour les compléter."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessun dato biometrico. Importa la tua esportazione WHOOP (e Apple Health se ce l'hai) in Sorgenti dati per popolare questa sezione."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Пока нет биометрических данных. Импортируйте данные WHOOP, а также Apple Здоровье, если они у вас есть, в разделе «Источники данных»."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暂无生物数据。请在「数据来源」中导入你的 WHOOP 导出文件（如果有的话还可导入 Apple 健康）来填充这里。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暫無生物數據。請在「資料來源」中匯入你的 WHOOP 匯出檔案（如果有的話還可匯入 Apple 健康）來填充這裡。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No caffeine logged. Log an intake to see an estimate.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessuna caffeina registrata. Registra un'assunzione per vedere una stima."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "未记录咖啡因。记录一次摄入以查看估算。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "未記錄咖啡因。記錄一次攝入以查看估算。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No chest strap? No problem. NOOP can run off only your Apple Watch. It reads your watch's data through Apple Health and works out your Charge, Rest, Effort and Fitness Age right here on your phone. Everything stays on the device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Niente fascia toracica? Nessun problema. NOOP può funzionare solo con il tuo Apple Watch. Legge i dati del tuo orologio tramite Apple Health e calcola la tua carica, il tuo riposo, lo sforzo e l'Età di forma fisica direttamente sul tuo telefono. Tutto resta sul dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "没有胸带？没问题。NOOP 可以仅靠你的 Apple Watch 运行。它通过 Apple 健康读取你手表的数据，并就在你的手机上计算出你的能量、休息、消耗和体能年龄。一切都留在设备上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "沒有胸帶？沒問題。NOOP 可以僅靠你的 Apple Watch 運行。它透過 Apple 健康讀取你手錶的資料，並就在你的手機上計算出你的能量、休息、消耗和體能年齡。一切都留在裝置上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No clear reading yet": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna lettura chiara"
          }
