            "value": "無資料"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No data for these metrics in %@. Widen the range or pick metrics you've logged.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Keine Daten für diese Metriken in %@. Erweitere den Bereich oder wähle Metriken, die du erfasst hast."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No data for these metrics in %@. Widen the range or pick metrics you've logged."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No hay datos para estas métricas en %@. Amplía el rango o elige métricas que hayas registrado."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pas de données pour ces métriques dans %@. Élargissez la plage ou choisissez des métriques que vous avez enregistrées."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessun dato per queste metriche in %@. Amplia l'intervallo o scegli metriche che hai registrato."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Нет данных по этим показателям за %@. Расширьте диапазон или выберите показатели, которые уже записывались."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ 内这些指标没有数据。请扩大范围，或选择你已记录的指标。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ 內這些指標沒有資料。請擴大範圍，或選擇你已記錄的指標。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No data for today. Was your strap worn and connected overnight?": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessun dato per oggi. La tua fascia era indossata e connessa durante la notte?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今天没有数据。你的手环整晚都佩戴并保持连接了吗？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今天沒有資料。你的手環整晚都佩戴並保持連接了嗎？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No days yet where both NOOP and your phone counted steps. Once your phone logs a few days alongside the strap, they'll appear here so you can see how close the estimate is.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessun giorno in cui sia NOOP che il tuo telefono abbiano contato i passi. Una volta che il tuo telefono registrerà qualche giorno insieme alla fascia, appariranno qui così potrai vedere quanto è precisa la stima."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "还没有 NOOP 和你手机同时统计步数的日期。一旦你的手机与手环一起记录了几天，它们就会出现在这里，让你看到估算有多接近。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "還沒有 NOOP 和你手機同時統計步數的日期。一旦你的手機與手環一起記錄了幾天，它們就會出現在這裡，讓你看到估算有多接近。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No drinks logged yet. Tap Sip, Cup or Bottle to start.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna bevanda registrata. Tocca Sorso, Tazza o Bottiglia per iniziare."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未记录任何饮品。点击「一口」「一杯」或「一瓶」开始。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未記錄任何飲品。點擊「一口」「一杯」或「一瓶」開始。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No earlier night stored yet. Earlier nights sync in the morning.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna notte precedente salvata. Le notti precedenti si sincronizzano al mattino."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未存储更早的夜晚。更早的夜晚会在早晨同步。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未儲存更早的夜晚。更早的夜晚會在早晨同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No folder chosen yet. Pick one your cloud app already syncs, or any local folder.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna cartella scelta. Scegline una che la tua app cloud già sincronizza, oppure una qualsiasi cartella locale."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未选择文件夹。选择一个你的云应用已在同步的文件夹，或任意本地文件夹。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚未選擇資料夾。選擇一個你的雲端應用程式已在同步的資料夾，或任意本地資料夾。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No history yet.": {
      "localizations": {
