    "No nightly skin-temp value": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessun valore notturno della temperatura cutanea"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无夜间皮肤温度数值"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無夜間皮膚溫度數值"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No nights here yet. Import your WHOOP export in Data Sources to see every night, your sleep stages and trends straight away. Or open Intelligence to see last night computed from the strap after you wear it to bed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch keine Nächte hier. Importiere deinen WHOOP-Export unter Datenquellen, um sofort jede Nacht, deine Schlafphasen und Trends zu sehen. Oder öffne Intelligenz, um die letzte Nacht aus dem Strap berechnet zu sehen, nachdem du ihn nachts getragen hast."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No nights here yet. Import your WHOOP export in Data Sources to see every night, your sleep stages and trends straight away. Or open Intelligence to see last night computed from the strap after you wear it to bed."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aún no hay noches aquí. Importa tu exportación de WHOOP en Fuentes de datos para ver cada noche, tus fases de sueño y tendencias de inmediato. O abre Inteligencia para ver la noche anterior calculada desde la pulsera después de llevarla puesta a dormir."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pas encore de nuits ici. Importez votre export WHOOP dans Sources de données pour voir chaque nuit, vos stades de sommeil et tendances immédiatement. Ou ouvrez Intelligence pour voir la nuit dernière calculée depuis le bracelet après l'avoir porté au lit."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna notte qui. Importa la tua esportazione WHOOP in Sorgenti dati per vedere subito ogni notte, le fasi del sonno e gli andamenti. Oppure apri Intelligenza per vedere la scorsa notte calcolata dalla fascia dopo averla indossata a letto."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Пока нет данных о сне. Импортируйте данные WHOOP в разделе «Источники данных», чтобы сразу увидеть все ночи, стадии сна и тренды. Или откройте «Аналитику», чтобы увидеть данные за последнюю ночь после сна с браслетом."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里还没有夜间记录。请在「数据来源」中导入你的 WHOOP 导出文件，即可立即查看每一晚、你的睡眠阶段和趋势。或者在你佩戴手环入睡后，打开「智能」查看根据手环计算出的昨晚数据。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這裡還沒有夜間記錄。請在「資料來源」中匯入你的 WHOOP 匯出檔案，即可立即查看每一晚、你的睡眠階段和趨勢。或者在你佩戴手環入睡後，打開「智慧」查看根據手環計算出的昨晚數據。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No nights with sleep data yet — your ledger fills in as you wear the strap to bed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna notte con dati sul sonno, il tuo registro si riempie man mano che indossi la fascia a letto."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚无有睡眠数据的夜晚 — 随着你佩戴手环入睡，你的记录会逐渐填满。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "尚無有睡眠資料的夜晚 — 隨著你佩戴手環入睡，你的記錄會逐漸填滿。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No overlap yet between this marker and %@. Log a few more readings (and keep wearing your strap).": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessuna sovrapposizione tra questo marcatore e %@. Registra qualche altra lettura (e continua a indossare la tua fascia)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此标记与 %@ 之间尚无重叠。请多记录几条读数（并继续佩戴你的手环）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此標記與 %@ 之間尚無重疊。請多記錄幾筆讀數（並繼續佩戴你的手環）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
