          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Пока нет истории стресса. Импортируйте данные WHOOP в разделе «Источники данных», чтобы увидеть её."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暂无压力历史。请在「数据来源」中导入你的 WHOOP 导出文件来查看。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暫無壓力歷史。請在「資料來源」中匯入你的 WHOOP 匯出檔案來查看。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No workout, stress, recovery, sleep, HRV, resting-HR, strain, respiratory-rate or skin-temp readings fell inside %@. Wear your strap a few more days, or pick a wider range, then export again.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nessuna lettura di allenamento, stress, recupero, sonno, HRV, FC a riposo, carico, frequenza respiratoria o temperatura cutanea è rientrata in %@. Indossa la tua fascia per qualche altro giorno, o scegli un intervallo più ampio, poi esporta di nuovo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在 %@ 内没有任何锻炼、压力、恢复、睡眠、HRV、静息心率、强度、呼吸频率或皮肤温度读数。请再佩戴手环几天，或选择更宽的范围，然后重新导出。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在 %@ 內沒有任何鍛鍊、壓力、恢復、睡眠、HRV、靜息心率、強度、呼吸頻率或皮膚溫度讀數。請再佩戴手環幾天，或選擇更寬的範圍，然後重新匯出。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No workouts yet. They come from your WHOOP and Apple Health history. Import in Data Sources to bring them in — or add one you tracked elsewhere.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessun allenamento. Provengono dalla cronologia del tuo WHOOP e di Apple Health. Importa in Sorgenti dati per acquisirli, oppure aggiungine uno che hai tracciato altrove."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暂无锻炼记录。它们来自你的 WHOOP 和 Apple 健康历史。请在「数据来源」中导入以引入它们 — 或添加一次你在别处追踪的锻炼。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "暫無鍛鍊記錄。它們來自你的 WHOOP 和 Apple 健康歷史。請在「資料來源」中匯入以引入它們 — 或新增一次你在別處追蹤的鍛鍊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No workouts yet. They come from your WHOOP and Apple Health history. Import in Data Sources to bring them in.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch keine Workouts. Sie stammen aus deinem WHOOP- und Apple-Health-Verlauf. Importiere sie unter Datenquellen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No workouts yet. They come from your WHOOP and Apple Health history. Import in Data Sources to bring them in."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aún no hay entrenamientos. Provienen de tu historial de WHOOP y Apple Health. Impórtalos en Fuentes de datos para añadirlos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pas encore d'entraînements. Ils proviennent de votre historique WHOOP et Apple Santé. Importez dans Sources de données pour les intégrer."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora nessun allenamento. Provengono dalla cronologia del tuo WHOOP e di Apple Health. Importa in Sorgenti dati per aggiungerli."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
