    "Recovery weighs your HRV against your personal baseline (~60%), resting heart rate (~20%), sleep performance (~15%) and respiration (~5%). Day strain is a 0–21 cardiovascular load from time in heart-rate zones. Sleep is staged from movement and heart rate. Everything is computed here from the strap's raw data , it works for any day NOOP collected raw streams.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Die Erholung gewichtet deine HRV gegenüber deiner persönlichen Basislinie (~60 %), die Ruheherzfrequenz (~20 %), die Schlafleistung (~15 %) und die Atmung (~5 %). Die Tagesbelastung ist eine kardiovaskuläre Last von 0–21 aus der Zeit in Herzfrequenzzonen. Der Schlaf wird aus Bewegung und Herzfrequenz in Phasen eingeteilt. Alles wird hier aus den Rohdaten des Straps berechnet , es funktioniert für jeden Tag, an dem NOOP Rohdaten erfasst hat."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Recovery weighs your HRV against your personal baseline (~60%), resting heart rate (~20%), sleep performance (~15%) and respiration (~5%). Day strain is a 0–21 cardiovascular load from time in heart-rate zones. Sleep is staged from movement and heart rate. Everything is computed here from the strap's raw data , it works for any day NOOP collected raw streams."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La recuperación pondera tu VFC frente a tu línea base personal (~60%), la frecuencia cardíaca en reposo (~20%), el rendimiento del sueño (~15%) y la respiración (~5%). El esfuerzo del día es una carga cardiovascular de 0–21 según el tiempo en zonas de frecuencia cardíaca. El sueño se clasifica a partir del movimiento y la frecuencia cardíaca. Todo se calcula aquí a partir de los datos en bruto de la pulsera: funciona para cualquier día en el que NOOP recopiló flujos en bruto."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La récupération pondère votre VFC par rapport à votre référence personnelle (~60%), fréquence cardiaque au repos (~20%), performance du sommeil (~15%) et respiration (~5%). L'effort du jour est une charge cardiovasculaire de 0 à 21 basée sur le temps dans les zones de fréquence cardiaque. Le sommeil est stagé à partir du mouvement et de la fréquence cardiaque. Tout est calculé ici à partir des données brutes du bracelet , cela fonctionne pour chaque jour où NOOP a collecté des flux bruts."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il recupero pesa il tuo HRV rispetto alla tua linea di base personale (~60%), la frequenza cardiaca a riposo (~20%), la prestazione del sonno (~15%) e la respirazione (~5%). Il carico giornaliero è un carico cardiovascolare da 0 a 21 basato sul tempo trascorso nelle zone di frequenza cardiaca. Il sonno viene suddiviso in fasi a partire da movimento e frequenza cardiaca. Tutto viene calcolato qui dai dati grezzi della fascia, funziona per qualsiasi giorno in cui NOOP ha raccolto i flussi grezzi."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Восстановление рассчитывается на основе вашей ВСР относительно личной нормы (~60%), пульса в покое (~20%), качества сна (~15%) и частоты дыхания (~5%). Дневная нагрузка , это сердечно-сосудистая нагрузка от 0 до 21, рассчитанная по времени в пульсовых зонах. Стадии сна определяются по движению и пульсу. Всё рассчитывается здесь, на основе исходных данных браслета, и работает для любого дня, когда NOOP собирал исходные потоки данных."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢复会将你的 HRV 与你的个人基线（约 60%）、静息心率（约 20%）、睡眠表现（约 15%）和呼吸（约 5%）进行加权。当日强度是根据在各心率区间的时间得出的 0–21 心血管负荷。睡眠则根据体动和心率分期。一切都在这里根据手环的原始数据计算——只要 NOOP 采集到原始数据流的任何一天都适用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢復會將你的 HRV 與你的個人基線（約 60%）、靜息心率（約 20%）、睡眠表現（約 15%）和呼吸（約 5%）進行加權。當日強度是根據在各心率區間的時間得出的 0–21 心血管負荷。睡眠則根據體動和心率分期。一切都在這裡根據手環的原始資料計算——只要 NOOP 採集到原始資料流的任何一天都適用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recovery, NOOP's Charge score, is led by your heart-rate variability measured against your own personal baseline. A chest strap streams beat-to-beat data densely all night, so it can learn that baseline fast. An Apple Watch instead samples HRV, a handful of readings through the day plus overnight, so the signal is real but sparser.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il recupero, il punteggio carica di NOOP, è guidato dalla variabilità della tua frequenza cardiaca misurata rispetto alla tua linea di base personale. Una fascia toracica trasmette dati battito per battito in modo fitto per tutta la notte, così può imparare velocemente quella linea di base. Un Apple Watch invece campiona l'HRV, qualche lettura durante il giorno più la notte, quindi il segnale è reale ma più rado."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢复，即 NOOP 的能量评分，主要由你的心率变异性相对于你个人基线的测量来主导。胸带整晚密集地串流逐拍数据，因此能快速学会该基线。而 Apple Watch 则是对 HRV 进行采样，全天加上夜间只有零星几次读数，所以信号是真实的，但更稀疏。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢復，即 NOOP 的能量評分，主要由你的心率變異性相對於你個人基線的測量來主導。胸帶整晚密集地串流逐拍資料，因此能快速學會該基線。而 Apple Watch 則是對 HRV 進行取樣，全天加上夜間只有零星幾次讀數，所以訊號是真實的，但更稀疏。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recovery, Test Centre, experimental probes, and backup. Tucked away to keep the everyday screen tidy.": {
      "localizations": {
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Recupero, Centro test, sonde sperimentali e backup. Messi da parte per mantenere ordinata la schermata di tutti i giorni."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢复、测试中心、实验性探测和备份。收纳于此，让日常界面保持整洁。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "恢復、測試中心、實驗性探測和備份。收納於此，讓日常畫面保持整潔。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
